 mid isolation\n   4. Verify cassette insertion with SpeI cut\n   5. Now re
 ady to insert HCR\n   6. ☒ Tapiwa will cross-check with Promega Subcloning
  Notebook (in\n      Zotero)\n4. Spinney opportunity\n   • help finish/wra
 p up experiments\n   • contribute to writing manuscript\n   • Tapiwa will 
 arrange separate mtg to discuss this project
